{
  "texts": [
    "We have not explicitly computed correlation functions so cannot comment on the higher genus case precisely.",
    "However, one finds S = 0 around the insertion points of (spectrally flowed) highest weight states, by computing the OPE with (3.10).",
    "The only remaining non-contractible cycles (at genus zero) are about {z * a }, which are removed from the worldsheet to study the theory in the given chart ξ + ̸ = 0.",
    "As in [52], to return to the full worldsheet and not merely a chart, we must introduce fictitious vertex operators at these points -the \"secret representations\" below.",
    "19 One can show thatJ + (z)β(w)e -2Φ(w) ∼ 0, J 3 (z)β(w)e -2Φ(w) ∼ 0, J -(z)β(w)e -2Φ(w) ∼ ∂ ∂w e -2Φ(w) z -w,such that S is invariant under J a (z)."
  ]
}